products.description:
Product name

Ultrasonic Adjustable Dog Flute

Product color Metallic

Applicable object Whole dog breed

Product material

Brass electroplated nickel

Product weight  12G

What's the difference between this and a regular whistle?

The sound blown by the dog flute belongs to ultrasound, which has a long propagation distance and is not disturbed by external sounds, which is very suitable for long-distance recall of dogs.

The sound of the dog whistle is not very loud, can the dog hear it?

Ultrasound is beyond the range of the human ear, so only the tubular sound of the dog's whistle can be heard. But the dog's ear can receive ultrasonic waves, and for dogs, it can receive bright and accurate instructions.

The dog doesn't respond when it hears it. What's going on?

Dogs are not born knowing how to play the dog whistle to return to their owners, which requires training.

Can I adjust the sound volume?

The size of the space in the rotating adjustment tube can be adjusted by adjusting the position of the nut to adjust the pitch of the sound, so as to achieve the purpose of adjusting the volume. Each dog has its own pitch, choose the pitch that the dog likes to use for training half the work, twice the effect.
